-j-nous-faisons-le-point-ensemble-sur-la-situation\/\">Blog de la Ligne J.<\/a>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","disruption_id":"b28d805c-7ad9-49ff-885a-8edfce118d76"},{"id":"2f394146-47ae-11f0-882a-0a58a9feac02","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20250612T185400","end":"20260831T023000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260326T115649","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"BLOQUANTE","tags":["Actualité"],"title":"Tramway T1 : Mesures de sécurité - Trafic interrompu","message":"<p>Trafic interrompu entre Asnières - Quatre Routes et Gare de Saint-Denis en raison de dégradations par un tiers. Reprise des circulations envisagée en fin d'été 2026.<\/p><p>Bus de remplacement entre Asnières–Gennevilliers–Les Courtilles et Mairie de Villeneuve-la-Garenne.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic interrompu","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01389","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72323","name":"Saint-Denis (Saint-Denis)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72267","name":"Asnières - Quatre Routes (Asnières-sur-Seine)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01389","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72267","name":"Asnières - Quatre Routes (Asnières-sur-Seine)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:72323","name":"Saint-Denis (Saint-Denis)"}}],"disruption_id":"368a646e-34a5-11f0-8b29-0a58a9feac02"},{"id":"558932de-ed6e-4d7e-8d18-c3268de92ca8","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260604T054400","end":"20260604T100000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260604T054654","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Tramway T4 -  : Trafic perturbé sur toute la ligne","message":"<p>Le trafic est perturbé sur toute la ligne T4.<br>&nbsp;<\/p><p>Motif : Condition de départ non réunies.<\/p>","disruption_id":"f4c35d8e-7c8d-495f-afd9-76da2cf396a6"},{"id":"b4f11d79-23cc-49ea-a3ea-979fa5457150","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260413T050000","end":"20260614T010000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260604T050058","cause":"TRAVAUX","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"Travaux du lundi 13 avril 2026 au 12 juin 202